                    "text": "Vanilla OS X 10.4 \"Tiger\" install.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Also tried with X11 installed but no luck.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "This is not really a \"Minor\" bug.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "  It is a big headache to minimise the\napplication and open up Thunderbird every time.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "  Particularly if you do it a\nhundred times a day (literally!)", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
