        {
            "date": "2009-01-12 14:27:10", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Lack of ability to perform actions like this on the Mac is a huge hole.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": " If I\ncan set Thunderbird as the default mail client, I should be able to have the\nprogram integrate with the operating system better than it does.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "As-is, Thunderbird is inaccessible to other programs.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " External apps (like the\nrecently-released Picasa beta, Office, iCal, Growl, etc.)", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " can create new mail\nmessages, with attachments, out of the box.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Thunderbird doesn't even have an\nextension to allow this function on the Mac.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": " This works on Windows - if I set\nthe program as my default, external apps can fire Tbird to mail things using\nMAPI.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "This should have been pushed for TB2, it really ought to be an available\nfunction in TB3.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Lack of system integration is a major problem.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Tbird cannot be\nused as an enterprise app if it can't accept mail requests from commonly used\nprograms such as Office, etc.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "The workaround (open Tbird, new message, then attach) is three steps too many\nfor the casual user, and an obstacle to adoption.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": " If it is harder than clicking\nthe \"Send as email\" button in Word, most Mac users are going to default to Mail\nor Entourage instead.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "Joshua Nixon", 
