                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I haven't got time at the moment to work on this, however I have just had a\nlook around and got some ideas on how to fix this bug.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " I'm dumping them here so\nthat someone may by able to take them on, or I may get time in a few months.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "It looks like two things are required:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "1) An NSServices section in Info.plist (e.g. see Camino's\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "http://mxr.mozilla.org/seamonkey/source/camino/Info-Camino.plist.in also\nMail.app's Info.plist also has some ideas).\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "2) Call to NSApp setServicesProvider with a class to implement the appropriate\nfunction (e.g. see Camino's url handler:\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "http://bonsai.mozilla.org/cvsblame.cgi?", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "file=mozilla/camino/src/application/MainController.mm&rev=1.278&mark=156,934-962#156\nnote: two sections marked).\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "I believe that is all, but there are other references on the internet that may\nneed to be consulted as well.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
